help.title: Silvanus Help
help.info:
Silvanus is a dedicated companion bot designed for Grow A Tree, the popular Discord clicker game. With Silvanus by your side, you can take your tree-growing adventure to new heights! Enjoy customizable notifications, effortless tree height comparisons, and handy math features to optimize your gameplay.

[Privacy Policy](https://assets.vfsh.dev/privacy.txt)
help.topggBody: Vote and leave a review for Silvanus [on Top.gg](https://top.gg/bot/521624335119810561)
help.setup:
For the most up to date guides and information, check out the Silvanus Support Wiki - https://silvanus.vfsh.dev/
[Silvanus Setup Guide](https://silvanus.vfsh.dev/en/setup)

Need help and can't reach me on Discord? Send an email to SilvanusDev@gmail.com and I'll get back to you ASAP.
help.longDescription:
Silvanus, the ultimate companion bot for Grow A Tree, takes your tree-growing journey to the next level. Are you tired of cluttered channels filled with notifications? Silvanus has you covered! With its unique notification relay system, Silvanus listens for Grow A Tree's notifications in a hidden channel and sends customized, auto-deleting notifications to the channels of your choice. Customize your notifications and keep your server clean and organized.

Silvanus simplifies leaderboard tree height comparisons with a simple command. No more manual calculations or guesswork. Silvanus shows you exactly how far you are from the next tree on the leaderboard, allowing you to gauge your progress effortlessly.
help.allCommands:
</compare:1077058896469966889> - Compare your tree to others on the leaderboard
</relay set:1077322799032578152> - Setup a Notification Relay for the first time
</relay update:1077322799032578152> - Update an already configured Notification Relay
</relay disable:1077322799032578152> - Disable the Notification Relay
</rolemenu:1077058896469966892> - Send a self-assignable role menu for relay pings
</watertime:1077058896469966895> - Calculates the time between waters for a tree of a given height
</timetoheight:1077058896469966894> - Calculates how long it would take a tree to grow to a given height
</setup compare:1077058896469966893> - Set the channels to use with </compare:1077058896469966889>
</setup view:1077058896469966893> - View your server's configuration
</setup reset:1077058896469966893> - Delete your server's configuration
</help:1077058896469966890> - Displays the bot's help page
